data.description: Mayfair neighborhood living at its finest!!! Bring your decorating ideas to this huge brick 2 flat with a finished basement.  The open concept 2nd floor unit has 3 full sized bedrooms, hardwood flooring throughout along with in unit washer & dryer, separate gar forced furnace and central a/c.  The first floor also features hardwood flooring throughout huge kitchen area, separate gas forced furnace & central air conditioner.  There is a separate side entrance for the finished basement that is currently being used for in law living that has its separate furnace and central a/c unit There's 3 tankless hot water tanks for endless water supply to the building.  A 2-car garage sits on the paved backyard area.  Bring your decorating ideas to this fantastic located 2 flat with a fully finished basement.  Excellent income potential!!!
